quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,101,"And how do you disbelieve and on you are (being) read/recited God`s verses/evidences and in (among) you (is) His messenger, and who holds fast/takes protection with God, so he had been guided to a straight/direct road/way"
  3,102,"You, you those who believed fear and obey God, His real/deserved fear and obedience, and do not die (E) except and you are submitters/surrenderers/Moslems"
  3,103,"And hold fast/take protection with God`s rope/covenant , all together, and do not separate, and mention/remember God`s blessing on you when you were enemies, so He united between your hearts , so you became with His blessings brothers, and you were on (the) edge/brink (of) a pit/hole from the fire, so He rescued/saved you from it, like that God clarifies for you His signs/verses/evidences, maybe/perhaps you be guided"
  3,104,"And to be (E) (should be) from you a nation , (who) call to the good , and they order/command with the kindness/known , and they forbid/prevent from the awfulness/obscenity , and those, they are the successful/winners"
  3,105,"And do not be like those who separated and differed , from after what the evidences came to them, and those, for them (is a) great torture"
  3,106,"A day (when) faces whiten and faces blacken, so but whose faces blackened, (will be told): \"Did you disbelieve after your faith/belief? So taste/experience the torture because (of) what you were disbelieving"
  3,107,"And but those whose faces whitened, so in God`s mercy, they are in it immortally/eternally"
  3,108,"Those are God`s signs/verses/evidences, We read/recite it on you with the truth , and God does not want injustice/oppression to the creations altogether/(universes)"